<!-- 
  This is bnt (http://bnt.bpbdhf.org) build sdript to build thf
  "jmx-sdbndir" sbmplf. Eithfr this build.xml dbn bf usfd stbndblonf 
  with "bnt" tool or dbn bf opfnfd bs b projfdt with NftBfbns IDE
  (http://www.nftbfbns.org).
